{"tid":1785737,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［同路人限定］手工製作班","createTime":"2019-12-16T15:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T20:18:56.000Z","uid":134099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7b4f475e7486c0da688b61608f5e162c05d0d01","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:20:15.000Z","msg":"是咁的，由6月以來，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">已經有超過6000位手足被捕</span></strong></span><br />\n趁呢排未打大交，我同一班手足諗住喺今年年宵做返啲嘢<br />\n而家一星期會有三日平日開放手工制作工作坊 (可自選時段)<br />\n(唔分男女，咩類型手作都有，有專人教，步驟唔會太複雜，有耐性唔厭煩就得)<br />\n呢啲手作之後會放去年宵度賣 (詳情呢度唔講太多，tg再傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n名額: 暫時搵住30位手足義務幫手先<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">被捕手足、俾屋企斷水斷糧手足、中學生手足優先</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">有金主可以提供交通同食飯津貼</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">所有收入會不扣除成本, 全數捐去支援前線手足嘅組織</span></strong><br />\n如果你身邊識有朋友有類似嘅情況，可以幫手send呢個post畀佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有興趣可以tg我: <a href=\"https://t.me/meowynott\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmeowynott&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7tKNpY%2BoLPIqDl3on0Jjdx4%3D&h=7505f983\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/meowynott</a> (睇到之後會盡快覆你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>問: 係咪請免費勞工?</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>答: 我哋都係一班後生仔女，大家都係無私咁貢獻自己嘅時間，無諗過賺錢。同埋你嚟到，就當你係手足咁看待</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問: 係咪食人血饅頭，消費緊場運動?</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong> 嚴格嚟講係，但香港抗爭就係一回咁諷刺嘅事，必然有好多同路人淨係畀錢當支持，亦有人花幾十萬去買民主女神像......年宵係勢在必行嘅活動，我哋嘅出現只係令到啲錢可以落到去最需要嘅手足身上</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">問: 驚唔驚有鬼?</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">答: 我哋同大家一樣驚，但會盡量fact check，慢慢熟絡咗就會好啲，同埋都係整手作啫</span></strong>"},{"pid":"483fcee70629a7e5fdef25f12800a79dc22dc5d9","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T15:20:35.000Z","msg":"頭先開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6d576d679ca71c36f279a4b7b1021615bfdbac5","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"42cbacb5df9ecd6a4fdbdfccd1806b1594c29f98","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:48:15.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"32009c49bae12c9ff45551774498ab0bc83544e5","tid":1785737,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e70cc59c487e0a7ca0c467547c50baad87897dd0","tid":1785737,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91ddb67ac1dd68fdc44edb41830bb1e3997633ef","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32009c49bae12c9ff45551774498ab0bc83544e5","tid":1785737,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T20:05:03.000Z","msg":"想搵班被捕手足圍爐做義工<br />\n冇被狗咬嗰啲咪出返去繼續抗爭<br />\n<br />\n你有咩問題？"},{"pid":"f90b160d0849baaac216d23759c60993aa1fc8f1","tid":1785737,"uid":134099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"32009c49bae12c9ff45551774498ab0bc83544e5","tid":1785737,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T19:55:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T20:18:56.000Z","msg":"義工唔代表冇門檻㗎<br />\n想識返相關人士都唔得？"}]}